<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git init
git remote add origin https://github.com/agent18/emacs-config.git
git pull origin master
git config user.email "thetj09@gmail.com"
git config user.name "agent18"
git push --set-upstream origin master
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Now need to setup the permanent PAT as follows: only one command as the other aspects are done earlier.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git config credential.helper /usr/share/doc/git/contrib/credential/libsecret/git-credential-libsecret
</code></pre></div></div>

